{
  "chapters": [
    {
      "description": "Open the original 1984 manga and meet a young Goku living alone in the woods, then watch Bulma arrive hunting the Dragon Balls. See how Akira Toriyama sets up the entire saga with one strange kid, one talking radar, and seven magic orbs.",
